Professional Support Lawyer, 3+PQE, Dubai
Professional Support Lawyer, 3+PQE, Dubai
Location:  --Dubai
This top tier global law firm is looking for a PSL to join its highly regarded office in Dubai. The ideal candidate will be a mid-senior level Associate, and you will primarily be based within the corporate team.
You will be responsible for maintaining up to date industry knowledge of relevant areas of law, drafting complex documents in English and be pro-active in proposing solutions to internal clients and colleagues. You will be an expert within your field of law, recognise changes that require the amendment of precedents and take responsibility for organising and running internal meetings and training programmes. You will also take an active role in business development, alongside the Partners and manage the administrative side of client pitches as well as organising and initiating client development activities.
For further details, candidates fulfilling the above criteria are invited to send their CV in complete confidence to
